contentrichtext.text: '''House of Delegates''' can refer to: * the [[United States House of Delegates (disambiguation)|lower house of the legislature in three U.S. states]] * the [[House of Delegates of Palau|lower house]] of the Palau National Congress * the governing body of several professional organizations, particularly medical ones such as the [[American Medical Association]] and its state affiliates * the [[Legislative_Assembly_of_Puerto_Rico#History|legislature]] of Puerto Rico between 1900 and 1917 * the [[House of Delegates (South Africa)|legislative chamber]] reserved for the Indian population of South Africa, in the tricameral Parliament between 1984 and 1994 [[Category:Legislatures]] {{disambig}}
